## 🌍 IT Everywhere Concept

Today, Information Technology (IT) exists in almost every industry.

**Example:** Travel platforms like *MakeMyTrip*

### How Web Applications Work

1. User opens the website  
2. Enters travel details (Delhi → Bangalore)  
3. System processes the request  
4. Results are fetched from the database  

👉 This demonstrates how modern web applications work behind the scenes.

