## 🧠 Key Takeaways

- VNet = Network  
- Subnet = Segmentation  
- NSG = Security  
- VM = Compute  

---

## ⚠️ Real-World Issues

- NSG block → App not accessible  
- Wrong subnet → Communication failure  
- No public IP → No internet access  

